ml#AddCommMonoid\">AddCommMonoid</a> <span class=\"fn\">M</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Basic.html#WickContraction\">WickContraction</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">φs</span>.<a href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.insertIdx\">insertIdx</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">(↑<span class=\"fn\">i</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">φ</span>)</span>.<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.length\">length</a></span></span> → <span class=\"fn\">M</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\">∑ <span class=\"fn\">c</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Basic.html#WickContraction\">WickContraction</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">φs</span>.<a href=\"./Init/Data/List/Basic.html#List.insertIdx\">insertIdx</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">(↑<span class=\"fn\">i</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">φ</span>)</span>.<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.length\">length</a></span></span>, <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">f</span> <span class=\"fn\">c</span></span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a>   <span class=\"fn\">∑ <span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Basic.html#WickContraction\">WickContraction</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">φs</span>.<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.length\">length</a></span></span>, <span class=\"fn\">∑ <span class=\"fn\">k</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <span class=\"fn\">↥<span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Uncontracted.html#WickContraction.uncontracted\">uncontracted</a></span></span></span>, <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">f</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/InsertAndContract.html#WickContraction.insertAndContract\">insertAndContract</a> <span class=\"fn\">φ</span> <span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span> <span class=\"fn\">k</span>)</span></span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"For a list `φs` of `𝓕.FieldOp`, a Wick contraction `φsΛ` of `φs`, an element `φ` of\n`𝓕.FieldOp` and a `i ≤ φs.length` then a sum over\nWick contractions of `φs` with `φ` inserted at `i` is equal to the sum over Wick contractions\n`φsΛ` of just `φs` and the sum over optional uncontracted elements of the `φsΛ`.\n\nIn other words,\n\n`∑ (φsΛ : WickContraction (φs.insertIdx i φ).length), f φsΛ`\n\nwhere `(φs.insertIdx i φ)` is `φs` with `φ` inserted at position `i`. is equal to\n\n`∑ (φsΛ : WickContraction φs.length), ∑ k, f (φsΛ ↩Λ φ i k) `.\n\nwhere the sum over `k` is over all `k` in `Option φsΛ.uncontracted`. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/InsertAndContract.html#WickContraction.insertLift_sum","kind":"theorem","line":290,"name":"WickContraction.insertLift_sum","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L290-L310"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/InsertAndContract.html#WickContraction.insert_fin_eq_self\"><span class=\"name\">WickContraction</span>.<span class=\"name\">insert_fin_eq_self</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">φ</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a h